    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a time capsule of pure automotive elegance. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a masterclass in design, finished in a hue that captures the fleeting gold of a Tuscan sunset. Every curve tells a story of prestige, and the interior\u2014a sanctuary of hand-stitched leather and polished wood\u2014remains a testament to an era when craftsmanship was a religion. To drive it is to command the wind itself, a silent symphony of power and poise that turns every mundane commute into a grand tour. It is, quite simply, perfection preserved in amber, waiting for its next curator to write the next glorious chapter.",
      "price": 48500.0,
